{"tid":2218061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬道立又講大話　黃之鋒案　學過刑事法律101都知阻嚇非加刑理由","createTime":"2020-09-26T02:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T05:28:21.000Z","uid":261647,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bd30c953e0c84d3d8dd730b103c7069bb0584e93","tid":2218061,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:45:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2842391375996935\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2842391375996935&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=f331857f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2842391375996935</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：黃鵹<br />\n<br />\n裁判官濫權拒絕保釋係基於「加刑十倍」上訴庭黃之鋒案。<br />\n<br />\n學過刑事法律101都會知道阻嚇唔係加刑嘅理由，只係量刑嘅多種目的其中之一。「各種目的一併考慮￼」同「只考慮唯一貼切目的」應該係相近，唔會相差10倍￼。量刑目的冇必然之輕重，只有同事實貼切同遙遠嘅分別。<br />\n<br />\n「阻嚇等同加刑十倍」本身就係馬道立口中嘅所謂政治，唔係法律。更準確嘅標籤係武斷 arbitrariness。馬道立確認黃之鋒案，但係取巧放黃之鋒，呃鬼佬法官，即係所有嘢都係佢搞出來。佢仲夠膽扮嘢，真係去死啦大話精。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2842411352661604&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2842411352661604%26set%3Da.1403846723184748%26type%3D3&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=8b736482\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2842411352661604&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n馬道立篇文明顯係喺度獻媚。蘋果日報頭版話咩反駁左報，真係精神病。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2842413532661386&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2842413532661386%26set%3Da.1403846723184748%26type%3D3&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=e0363600\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2842413532661386&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n馬道立篇文又講大話，「加刑十倍」將正常化。<br />\n<br />\n「加刑十倍」唔係正統阻嚇目的，亦唔係「為了達致某一目的會判處較重的刑罰」。<br />\n<br />\n同樣，所謂輕判只係跟英國案例嘅水平同香港人常識，兼「考慮每宗案件中所有具體情況」。啲正常法官根本冇「著重更生」，亦冇表面上減刑，亦唔係拒絕正統阻嚇。<br />\n<br />\n「加刑十倍」扭曲、包裝做阻嚇先係無視一切法律。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2842418735994199\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2842418735994199&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=9ffb35e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2842418735994199</a><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，馬道立係大話精。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2842436559325750\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2842436559325750&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=f0d59bf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2842436559325750</a><br />\n<br />\n三個段落已經自相矛盾。量刑完全唔係法律問題，純粹係法官參照最高刑罰按比例同猜測民意決定。冇量刑委員會嘅國家，係內閣透過委任法官來影響量刑。有量刑委員會嘅國家，都係內閣透過委任委員來影響量刑。<br />\n<br />\n#馬道立講大話系列<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTinHo Mak:<br />\n量刑由民意和事實判斷決定，不是法律判斷。上訴庭的職責係令各司法機關量刑標準趨向一致，唔係取代民意亦唔係取代事實判斷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2842440792658660\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2842440792658660&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=823cbc23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2842440792658660</a><br />\n<br />\n我可以確認香港人對香港司法嘅批評都係大致正確，絕對唔係馬道立老屈你哋嘅「在不熟知情況及欠缺適當基礎和理由，單憑純粹聲稱或斷章取義之事就批評法官及法院；只因案件的結果不合自己心意，便作出偏頗或違反基本原則的嚴重指稱」。"},{"pid":"cad49389e11b2001d76a7210320341fc8007f4d8","tid":2218061,"uid":40763,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T03:05:35.000Z","msg":"1年前<br />\n講左句馬道立 我屌你老母<br />\n成班衝出來咬人<br />\n得閒搵返個post bin c先"},{"pid":"8651127de383